### Send email using a React template
### Template type: reset-password
### Params: resetUrl (required), userName (optional), language (optional: "en-US" | "pt-BR", default "pt-BR")
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/mail/send-template
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "recipient@example.com",
  "templateType": "reset-password",
  "params": {
    "resetUrl": "https://app.example.com/reset-password?token=abc123xyz",
    "userName": "John Doe",
    "language": "pt-BR"
  }
}

### Reset password email in English (language: en-US)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/mail/send-template
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "recipient@example.com",
  "subject": "Reset your password",
  "templateType": "reset-password",
  "params": {
    "resetUrl": "https://app.example.com/reset?token=abc123",
    "userName": "Jane",
    "language": "en-US"
  }
}

### Same request with custom subject (optional)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/mail/send-template
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "juliovianadev@gmail.com",
  "subject": "Redefinir sua senha - Agenda AI",
  "templateType": "reset-password",
  "params": {
    "resetUrl": "https://app.example.com/reset-password?token=goiabada",
    "userName": "Maria"
  }
}

### Minimal params for reset-password (userName optional)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/mail/send-template
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "user@gmail.com",
  "templateType": "reset-password",
  "params": {
    "resetUrl": "https://myapp.com/reset?token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..."
  }
}

### Login code email — LIGHT theme (params: validationCode, language, loginUrl, theme)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/mail/send-template
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "juliovianadev@gmail.com",
  "subject": "Seu código de login - Light",
  "templateType": "login-code",
  "params": {
    "validationCode": "abc-123",
    "language": "pt-BR",
    "loginUrl": "https://localhost:5173",
    "theme": "light"
  }
}

### Login code email — DARK theme
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/mail/send-template
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "juliovianadev@gmail.com",
  "subject": "Seu código de login - Dark",
  "templateType": "login-code",
  "params": {
    "validationCode": "xyz-789",
    "language": "pt-BR",
    "loginUrl": "https://localhost:5173",
    "theme": "dark"
  }
}
